{"tid":1548298,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【美軍吹雞】美國防長質疑中國有否履行「一國兩制」，呼籲歐洲共同對抗中俄","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T03:58:49.000Z","uid":305299,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6f0bac373362c97c42654cce9e4344b0c68db7","tid":1548298,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"美國國防部長埃斯珀呼籲歐洲盟國共同對抗中國和俄羅斯，阻止兩國擴大對全球影響力。他又<span style=\"color: red;\">提及香港近日的反修訂示威，質疑中國有否履行「一國兩制」</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正在英國訪問的美國國防部長埃斯珀，在倫敦出席英國智庫皇家聯合服務研究所，並發表演說，點名批評中國盜取科技，以強化軍事力量，並和俄羅斯加強在太空和網絡領域的發展，企圖影響國際秩序。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國防部長埃斯珀表示：「越趨明顯俄羅斯和中國企圖影響國際秩序，透過對其他國家的經濟、外交及安全決策取得否決權。」<br />\n<br />\n他又警告歐洲盟友不要過份依賴中國的貿易投資，令對方透過經濟影響力，控制其他國家甚至全球。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n埃斯珀說：「一個國家越是依賴中國在貿易的投資，他們將更易受到壓迫及懲罰的傷害，當他們做一些有違北京意願的事。」<br />\n<br />\n埃斯珀強調，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國不能夠袖手旁觀</span></span>，否則只會令這些國家變本加厲，削弱美國及歐洲處理未來國際衝突的能力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n埃斯珀亦提及香港近日因反修訂爆發的示威衝突，他指那些持續發聲、反對中共影響香港自主的人的遭遇有目共睹，質疑中國有沒有履行「一國兩制」。<br />\n<br />\n中方早前多次敦促美方立即停止干預香港事務，以免損害中美關係和香港繁榮穩定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=====傳送門=====<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5d72b0aee603837c40de6fb0/%E7%BE%8E%E9%98%B2%E9%95%B7%E7%B1%B2%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E7%9B%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%84-%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A2%E5%85%A9%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8A%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5d72b0aee603837c40de6fb0%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E7%259B%259F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%258A%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BF%2584-%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E5%258A%259B&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAXJTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=d65e0a1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5d72b0aee603837c40de6fb0/%E7%BE%8E%E9%98%B2%E9%95%B7%E7%B1%B2%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E7%9B%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%84-%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A2%E5%85%A9%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8A%9B</a>"},{"pid":"b0fe869f39aa27cde1d8629d03b100682d231065","tid":1548298,"uid":261530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e849de0f98b47bdb5aa739b8cd43e1e7e2a66637","tid":1548298,"uid":287449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:38:29.000Z","msg":"神早大把武警同解放軍扮警察啦，同六四除左冇坦克同真彈之外有咩分別"},{"pid":"3f2373c9b36a9c9afc3b56e1ace0c56e7091e570","tid":1548298,"uid":261937,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"國防部長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba5275326827af133151299b8e2d926ebe54396","tid":1548298,"uid":74155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"咁多位師弟歸位喇<br />\n美帝吹雞喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c990dee81e56684629f3a8b4bfcee92379920896","tid":1548298,"uid":20522,